hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I've been made redundant precio pastillas cytotec ecuador If Dan Whitcomb filed this story from L.A. (the dateline), he should be ashamed of himself for his lack of geographical knowledge of the Riverside County area. It is NOT, repeat NOT part of the high desert. It is NOT part of the low desert. The HIGH DESERT is the area of Victorville, Palmdale, Barstow NORTH of the City of San Bernardino in the county of the same name. Hemet borders SW Riverside County. Hardly the HIGH DESERT Same on Whitcomb and his desk editor. If he’s posted in So. Cal, double shame.
